description: This file contains test functions for a team routing system involving agents with different response models, including structured and unstructured outputs, using the Pydantic library for data validation.

classes.name: StockAnalysis
classes.description: Pydantic model representing stock analysis with symbol, company name, and analysis text.

classes.name: CompanyAnalysis
classes.description: Pydantic model representing company analysis with company name and analysis text.

classes.name: StockInfo
classes.description: Pydantic model representing stock information with symbol and price.

methods.name: test_route_team_multiple_response_models
methods.description: Test function verifying team routing with different response models for each agent, including assertions on response content and agent responses.

methods.name: test_route_team_mixed_structured_output
methods.description: Test function verifying team routing with mixed structured and unstructured outputs, including assertions on response content and agent responses.
